  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下这个系统的整体架构。核心是有五个主要组件：命令行工具CustomCli、桌面应用CustomApp、后端API服务CustomApi，还有两个库——CustomSdk和CustomLib。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，五个节点。先确认一下类型——CustomCli和CustomApp都是可执行程序吧？CustomApi也是独立运行的服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CustomCli是控制台程序，CustomApp是基于MAUI的桌面应用，CustomApi是ASP服务。另外两个CustomSdk和CustomLib是类库，不能独立运行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这五个类先创建出来，标注好类型。CustomCli和CustomApp我标成Executable，Sdk和Lib标成Lib。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来画依赖关系。CustomCli要引用CustomLib和CustomSdk，CustomApp只引用CustomSdk。注意CustomApp不直接引用CustomLib，而是通过Sdk间接使用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，CustomCli到Lib和Sdk都是虚线依赖，CustomApp到Sdk也是虚线。那Sdk和Api之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是关键部分。Sdk通过HTTP连接调用Api，需要画两条线：一条是实线表示HTTP连接，标注上\"HTTP connection\"；另一条虚线表示请求消息，标注\"Request message (JSON encoded)\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "请求方向是Sdk指向Api对吧？那响应呢，Api返回数据给Sdk？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，响应也要画，用带箭头的虚线从Api指向Sdk，标注\"Response message (JSON encoded)\"。注意响应和请求要用不同样式区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Sdk到Api的关系画好了，三条线：HTTP连接虚线、请求实线、响应箭头虚线。Api本身也要引用CustomLib对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Api到Lib也是using关系。还有CustomApp其实也要直接引用CustomLib，我刚才漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我补上了App到Lib的虚线。现在检查一遍：Sdk引用Lib，Api引用Lib，App引用Lib和Sdk，Cli引用Lib和Sdk。这样Lib被三个组件共用，Sdk被Cli和App共用，结构清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。最后把布局调成从左到右，让CustomCli和CustomApp放左边，Sdk居中，Api放右边，Lib可以放在下方作为基础层。这样整个数据流向就一目了然了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
